     34  0000 ????
     35  0000 ????						; Note: These macros use illegal opcodes.  To disable illegal opcode usage, 
     36  0000 ????						;   define the symbol NO_ILLEGAL_OPCODES (-DNO_ILLEGAL_OPCODES=1 on command-line).
